high_descs: turn left and walk forwards a bit so that the kitchen counter is on your right side
grab the blue plate off of the kitchen counter
turn around and walk enough so that the stove is on your left at the end of the hall, then walk to the stove at the end of the hall
place the blue plate in the microwave above the stove, let it microwave then take it back out
turn around and walk enough so that the fridge is on your right, then turn right and head to the fridge
place the plate inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved plate inside of the fridge

high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the counter.
Pick up the blue plate from the counter.
Turn around, walk towards the counter, and turn right towards the microwave above the stove.
Heat up the plate and take the plate out of the microwave.
Place the plate on the top shelf inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed blue plate inside the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the counter left of the fridge.
Pick up the blue plate on the counter.
Bring the plate to the microwave on the right.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Bring the heated plate to the fridge on the left.
Chill the plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Chill a heated plate in the fridge.
